description: This code was built to recode and analyze survey data. The recoding script was built in Python while the data analysis script was built in R. The recoding script takes the raw survey data text and converts it to a numeric coding scheme. The data analysis script conducts analyses recommended by the American Psychological Association (APA) for data of this type.
